column5: anybody fished beech lake?, whats in their to catch ice fishing? any info would be sweet
Is that Beech lake in Haliburton? Small population of lakers in there. You'd be better off hitting Maple or Boshkung/12Mile.
There's also a Beech Lake in the Bracebridge area.  If that's the lake you're talking about, you can expect to find all of your pan fish species there, as well as the odd Pickerel.
